Derivatives Documentation Services – Rechtsberatung SILAEVA ep GALKE (“DDS”) has been established to provide legal services in the fields of derivatives trading and documentation of the OTC (over-the-counter) and on-exchange traded derivatives.

DDS offers cost effective, professional and superior service related to the regulatory change that impacts the business area and the documentation outsourcing of the OTC negotiation/documentation of the derivatives, repurchase, stock lending transactions.

DDS understands the pressures and difficulties facing the new regulatory requirements in relation to the transactions to be traded on exchanges and we offer to the financial institutions our legal support during the transition period in dealing with queries on matters relating to MiFID, Dodd-Franck and EMIR Regulations and the technical implementation of these new regulatory requirements.

DDS offers reporting outsourcing solution of the derivative and repo transactions negotiation, OTC cleared and on-exchange related financial documentation & implementation into the systems  of the EMIR reporting & clearing requirements :  clearing member/client documentation: Clearing Member Disclosure documents, Portfolio Reconciliation Dispute Resolution and disclosure agreements, EMIR/Dodd-Franck Client Classification documents; Cleared Derivatives Execution Agreements, ISDA/FOA EMIR Reporting Delegation Agreements & related reporting documentation, ISDA/FOA Client Cleared OTC Derivatives Addendum, FOA Clearing Module Agreement;	
 Legal consultation on the compliance matters related to Financial Service Regulations (EU);
• Loan CSD/TRS (tailor made) structuring & negotiation.

